centos下安装opencv并用python调用cv2.so
第一步:安装cmake
---------------------------------------------------------------
yum install cmake
---------------------------------------------------------------
第二步:解决依赖
---------------------------------------------------------------
yum install gtk2-devel
yum install pkg-config
---------------------------------------------------------------
第三步:下载解压opencv到自定义的文件夹中
第四步:编译安装
---------------------------------------------------------------
cd opencv-dir #自定义
mkdir opencv
rm CMakeCaches.txt
cd opencv
cmake ..
make 
make install
---------------------------------------------------------------
第五步:进入opencv/lib，链接到/usr/lib、/lib、/usr/lib/python2.7/\
site-packages/
---------------------------------------------------------------
ln cv2.so /usr/lib
ln cv2.so /lib
ln cv2.so /usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages
---------------------------------------------------------------
第六步:验证
---------------------------------------------------------------
ipython
import cv2
---------------------------------------------------------------
